  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battlecaster is a top-down arena roguelike, fighting against challenging waves of enemies. Each enemy is lethal and can end your run quickly. Learn fast and think on your feet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/5b0afc8e281e148b66bfa5992bc6774e.poster.avif?t=1748095433\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/5b0afc8e281e148b66bfa5992bc6774e.webm?t=1748095433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/5b0afc8e281e148b66bfa5992bc6774e.mp4?t=1748095433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make strategic use of your powerful abilities to control the field and survive. After each round you'll have your pick from a handful of rewards to gain power, maximize your build and stats to be most effective in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/b982b99943e532a5747889dd1ee4fb9a.poster.avif?t=1748095433\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/b982b99943e532a5747889dd1ee4fb9a.webm?t=1748095433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/b982b99943e532a5747889dd1ee4fb9a.mp4?t=1748095433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike Arena Rush </strong>– You've found yourself in the heart of the storm. Defend yourself in an abyssal arena or die trying. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced action</strong><i> </i>– Display combat prowess and moment to moment decision making or face certain doom. You will be challenged by relentless enemies who will not give you an inch of breathing room. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Develop an arsenal<i> </i></strong>– Collect powerful items and upgrades along the way to gain your advantage. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/d6e73e836815d6b5fa3d68b712547ea9.poster.avif?t=1748095433\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/d6e73e836815d6b5fa3d68b712547ea9.webm?t=1748095433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355770/extras/d6e73e836815d6b5fa3d68b712547ea9.mp4?t=1748095433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Roguelike gameplay</strong> – Every run is different and small decisions will have large impacts on your success. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 enemies</strong> – Each acting filling a unique 'chess piece' role in the ring.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>50+ items</strong> – Arm yourself with the equipment of heroes fallen before you. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless waves</strong> – Increasingly difficult challenges to survive through.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>A true challenge.</strong><br></p></li></ul>",
